rows.label: tlk43300241_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Refugees from Acedia have landed
not far from Gwendle Repair Dock.

rows.label: tlk43300241_04_msg0002
rows.name:
That's Invidian hospitality for you.
We're all floored by Queen Lagert's
benevolence.

rows.label: tlk43300241_04_msg0003
rows.name:
The people of Fons Maim have also
accepted them, getting ready for a life
built side by side.

rows.label: tlk43300241_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Like the distribution center.
The sight moves me every time.
I want to immortalize it in my art.

rows.label: tlk43300241_04_msg0005
rows.name:
But in the middle of all that, there
are noble sons who... Ah, pardon me.
I was about to commit slander there!
